  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (*)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 10 (Spell Level 5)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 8</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 23 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 12 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 25</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> H, E *</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This technique works like Godai Taigeki: Shodan Jutsu, but has you fire a cone of elemental energies, dealing 6d6 damage of the appropriate type. This technique has the following variants.<br><br>- Hyouseidan no Jutsu (Hyouton) [Cold]: Material Focus - At least 15 cubic ft of snow or ice nearby.<br>- Kaenhoudan no Jutsu (Katon) [Fire]<br>- Raiseidan no Jutsu (Raiton) [Electric]<br>- Shinkuudan no Jutsu (Fuuton) [Wind]<br>- Suiseidan no Jutsu (Suiton) [Water]: Material Focus - At least 250 liters of water nearby.<br>- Tsuchihoudan (Doton) [Earth]: Material Focus - At least 250 lbs of earth, stone or mud nearby.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 1 Chakra to increase the damage by 1d6, up to 1d6 per level or 16d6 (whichever is lower).</p>\n\n",
